title: Infini. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: May 8th, 2015

Description:

A search-and-rescue team are transported through deep space to a distant mining colony to save the sole survivor of a biological outbreak. During their mission, they find a lethal weapon which is set to arrive on Earth within the hour.

Director: Shane Abbess

Writers: Shane Abbess, Brian Cachia

Actors: Daniel MacPherson, Luke Hemsworth, Grace Huang, Bren Foster, Luke Ford, Dwaine Stevenson

Genre: Science Fiction, Action and Adventure

Run Time: 1 hour 50 minutes
